<!-- MESSAGE FROM THE HOD -->
<section class="hod-message">
  <h2 class="hod-title">Message from the Head of Department</h2>
  <p class="hod-text">
    Dear Students and Esteemed Colleagues,<br><br>
    As we begin this new year 2026, it is with great pride and immense joy 
that I present this latest edition of our department newsletter. Every page 
captures the enthusiasm, innovation, and accomplishments that define our 
dynamic community of faculty and students. Over the past few months, 
our department has reached significant academic milestones, hosted 
inspiring events, and undertaken initiatives that truly reflect our spirit of 
excellence, collaboration, and leadership.br><br>

   I feel proud to announce that SRM Institute of Science and Technology 
has been honoured with the prestigious EC-Council Academia Partner 
Ambassador Award in the South Asia Zone. The award stands as a 
testament to the dedicated efforts of our faculty, students, and leadership 
in fostering innovation, professional certification, and global engagement 
in the field of cybersecurity. SpazorLabs, a student-led startup participated 
in Supercomputing India 2025 (SCI2025) under the prestigious NextGen 
HPC–AI–Quantum Experiential Learning Program. Thus we are progressing 
towards innovative works along with industry partnerships.<br><br>

 Our faculty members distinguished themselves through notable journal 
publications and patent contributions, strengthening our commitment 
to research and innovation. We are equally proud of our students, who 
continue to uphold our strong placement record by securing opportunities 
in reputed organizations such as ITC Infotech, Accenture, Deloitte, KPMG, 
Brutanix Studios, and AB InBev.<br><br>

 I sincerely appreciate the dedicated efforts of our contributors, faculty 
members, and students whose passion and commitment continually 
elevate the reputation of our department. May this edition encourage 
you to embrace new ideas, participate wholeheartedly, and continue 
contributing meaningfully to the vibrant life of our academic community.<br><br>

  </p>

  <div class="hod-signature">
    <p><b>Dr. M. Lakshmi</b></p>
    <p>Professor & Head,<br>Department of Networking and Communications,<br>
    SRM Institute of Science and Technology</p>
  </div>
</section>

